snippet.title: 3D ATTACK Emerson Arcadia undumped game RAW FOOTAGE
snippet.description: The only known un-dumped game for the Emerson Arcadia console family. Was released only in Italy. Only around 6 copies known to exist. Is a Zaxxon clone, but plays more like a 3D obstacle course. Holy Grail of Arcadia collecting.
